{"tid":112763,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋搞笑漫畫] 女魔王同魔法師日常之類","createTime":"2017-02-08T11:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T11:58:01.000Z","uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7163ba809219d9bc78884bc046db7e47627013b","tid":112763,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T11:48:26.000Z","msg":"想搵返套搞笑漫畫<br />\n係講個女魔王同班人打左一場<br />\n打到好勁搞到佢地傳送左去唔個咩空間<br />\n主要係講個魔法師同魔王仲有其他人啲日常<br />\n個魔法師成日恰個女魔王<br />\n個空間啲環境好似廢墟咁<br />\n但魔法師成日搵到啲女人底褲<br />\n<br />\n一開始得魔法師同魔王生活之後有其他一齊後 都係之前有份大戰個啲<br />\n<br />\n講到咁睇過應該個邊套<br />\n突然間好想睇返 有冇人知咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5a7f833a06626b83bb4a96ae1f8af2a2fc46c9","tid":112763,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2n5MSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2n5MSQ.jpg&h=017f4efc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9401afe4e2c78c0e074d8c293ace4cf2a29db19c","tid":112763,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2n5MSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2n5MSQ.jpg&h=017f4efc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先打魔王搜尋都冇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}